      "parameters": {
        "content": "🎯 End-to-End Sales Pipeline Workflow\n\nReceives new leads via a form submission, uses AI to \nscore them as hot or cold, sends personalized outreach \nto hot leads and nurture emails to cold leads. \nLogs all to CRM automatically.\n\nNodes:\n**Step 1**\n📝 On Form Submission — Receives new lead via form\n\n**Step 2**\n🤖 OpenAI — Scores lead from 1-100 as Hot or Cold\n\n**Step 3**\n⚙️ Code in JavaScript — Cleans and structures lead data\n\n**Step 4**\n🔀 IF — Routes hot leads vs cold leads\n\n**Step 5**\n✅ TRUE: OpenAI1 — Writes personalized hot lead outreach\n\n**Step 6**\n✅ TRUE: Code in JavaScript1 — Cleans hot lead email\n\n**Step 7**\n✅ TRUE: Gmail — Sends outreach draft to hot lead\n\n**Step 8**\n✅ TRUE: Gmail1 — Sends urgent alert to sales rep\n\n**Step 9**\n✅ TRUE: Code in JavaScript3 — Prepares CRM data\n\n**Step 10**\n✅ TRUE: Google Sheets — Logs hot lead to CRM\n\n**Step 11**\n❌ FALSE: OpenAI2 — Writes cold lead nurture email\n\n**Step 12**\n❌ FALSE: Code in JavaScript2 — Cleans cold lead email\n\n**Step 13**\n❌ FALSE: Gmail2 — Sends nurture draft to cold lead\n\n**Step 14**\n❌ FALSE: Code in JavaScript4 — Prepares CRM data\n\n**Step 15**\n❌ FALSE: Google Sheets1 — Logs cold lead to CRM",
